  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the hero of the local art scene in The Art Collector! Assume the role of an artist and dedicated friend, entrusted with preserving the community's art gallery. Your mentor, the venerable curator of the gallery, relies on your expertise to ensure its survival in the face of mounting challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Curate Your Destiny:</strong> Immerse yourself in the exhilarating world of art curation. Buy, sell, and master the art of negotiation to keep the gallery's doors open and the bills paid.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/4f40c0a03c1e2dc2014fa0f4b97edfe5.poster.avif?t=1729596441\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/4f40c0a03c1e2dc2014fa0f4b97edfe5.webm?t=1729596441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/4f40c0a03c1e2dc2014fa0f4b97edfe5.mp4?t=1729596441\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Personalized Spaces:</strong> Showcase your unique style by customizing both your gallery and home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/e086bf25164b10cba6b099a7131b7ed1.poster.avif?t=1729596441\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/e086bf25164b10cba6b099a7131b7ed1.webm?t=1729596441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/e086bf25164b10cba6b099a7131b7ed1.mp4?t=1729596441\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Artistic Expression:</strong> Unleash your creativity by crafting and selling your own masterpieces. Explore various mediums and styles to leave your mark on the art world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/98e74ceaa300dea9d1e2542b310c0cb0.poster.avif?t=1729596441\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/98e74ceaa300dea9d1e2542b310c0cb0.webm?t=1729596441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/98e74ceaa300dea9d1e2542b310c0cb0.mp4?t=1729596441\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Empower Local Talent:</strong> Forge meaningful connections with up-and-coming artists. Champion their work, provide exposure, and watch as they blossom into the stars of tomorrow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/3132898e67deffac3f7ee4b92f2546ea.poster.avif?t=1729596441\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/3132898e67deffac3f7ee4b92f2546ea.webm?t=1729596441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/3132898e67deffac3f7ee4b92f2546ea.mp4?t=1729596441\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience the Thrill of the Art World:</strong> Learn the intricate dance of supply and demand, where every sale and acquisition shapes the destiny of the gallery. Make strategic decisions, cultivate relationships, and navigate the ever-changing art market to ensure your success. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/779ec780efc4153148ffb8b8a909a417.poster.avif?t=1729596441\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/779ec780efc4153148ffb8b8a909a417.webm?t=1729596441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/779ec780efc4153148ffb8b8a909a417.mp4?t=1729596441\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Join the Journey:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a part of our passionate community of art enthusiasts and aspiring creators by joining our discord. Stay tuned for exciting updates, community events, and ongoing support as we continue to develop \"The Art Collector\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/3fd111b8002283a6e30de4b08f80ab96.poster.avif?t=1729596441\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/3fd111b8002283a6e30de4b08f80ab96.webm?t=1729596441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/3fd111b8002283a6e30de4b08f80ab96.mp4?t=1729596441\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the hero of the local art scene in The Art Collector! Assume the role of an artist and dedicated friend, entrusted with preserving the community's art gallery. Your mentor, the venerable curator of the gallery, relies on your expertise to ensure its survival in the face of mounting challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Curate Your Destiny:</strong> Immerse yourself in the exhilarating world of art curation. Buy, sell, and master the art of negotiation to keep the gallery's doors open and the bills paid.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/4f40c0a03c1e2dc2014fa0f4b97edfe5.poster.avif?t=1729596441\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/4f40c0a03c1e2dc2014fa0f4b97edfe5.webm?t=1729596441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/4f40c0a03c1e2dc2014fa0f4b97edfe5.mp4?t=1729596441\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Personalized Spaces:</strong> Showcase your unique style by customizing both your gallery and home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/e086bf25164b10cba6b099a7131b7ed1.poster.avif?t=1729596441\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/e086bf25164b10cba6b099a7131b7ed1.webm?t=1729596441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2986690/extras/e086bf25164b10c